node.title: 14-year-old Wellington boy found safe and well
node.description: Police thank the public for their assistance.
node.content: ["A 14-year-old boy\u00a0who went missing in the Wellington region on Wednesday has been located.", "Police say he was found \"safe and well\" and they'd like to thank the public for the assistance provided in locating him.", "Newshub was notified at 8:41pm that the boy had been found.", "Police and family had earlier been concerned about the wellbeing of the teen, who was last seen at his home in the suburb of Southgate at 4pm.", "\u00a0"]
